column1: #Text=These girls were set up by the producers [ and were asked ] devious questions about me .
#Text=I did not even know that anyone went through my personal belongings until I watched the show myself .
#Text=On TV , due to editing , it comes across as Alanna and Brandi deciding to be nosy and poke through your things .
#Text=They were asked questions such as , " Soooo , what do you think of all the candy that Andrea has in her suitcase ?
